{"tid":1326082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"秋天一到，抗爭威力double up","createTime":"2019-07-17T05:47:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T06:09:33.000Z","uid":267881,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"45ef8db65e310a2701daf410233c7579cd3f0e34","tid":1326082,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:47:10.000Z","msg":"飲水需求下降，減輕物資組壓力<br />\n體力消耗減慢，可打持久戰<br />\n黑衫著面，其他顏色tee打底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保皇狗為保選票不再保皇住<br />\n<br />\n政府拖延戰失效、分化戰失效、帶風向失效、輿論戰失敗、白色恐怖無效、得罪晒唔同界别，官員同警隊民望每況愈下，特首已經彈盡糧絕，四面楚歌，相反抗爭者愈來愈精良，天時地利人和<br />\n<br />\n為保護國家面子、習主席威望<br />\n請林奠於10月1號前完成五大訴求<br />\n（唔係承諾，係完成）<br />\n或者果斷戒嚴、用致命武力鎮壓、出動解放軍<br />\n<br />\n利申：忠黨愛國<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6365def234ef54baf2eb76deafd5dacd8c187b28","tid":1326082,"uid":76632,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:48:21.000Z","msg":"八月十五中秋食月餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用紙仔傳情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb04f704242bb7bb557ffca42fecf87013f4867e","tid":1326082,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:48:48.000Z","msg":"開<br />\n學了"},{"pid":"f75908de0b8b4eb083c6e610df7eb77cdfebc575","tid":1326082,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6365def234ef54baf2eb76deafd5dacd8c187b28","tid":1326082,"uid":76632,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:48:21.000Z","msg":"八月十五中秋食月餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用紙仔傳情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:49:12.000Z","msg":"不過7月21都要出金鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"817d10161a8ab24e20d3a056e6a871c0a7c98c71","tid":1326082,"uid":119408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-